{"word":"ἱλαρός","slug":"ἱλαρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἱλαρός</b></el> <el>(ἱ˘λᾰρός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἵλαος</el>\n<p/><i>cheerful, gay, merry, joyous</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>hilaris</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <el>τὸ ἱλαρόν  ἱλαρότης</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ρῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}